OL,3,CMinister: 'Funding for Jersey's health
OL,4,Cservice may have to change'
OL,6,FSpeaking exclusively to ITV News, he
OL,7,Fsays: "We have to be careful not to be
OL,8,Fover radical but the current plan is
OL,9,Fto restructure the health service.
OL,10,FSome work has already been done to
OL,11,Flook at other models.
OL,13,F"We need to design something that
OL,14,Fworks for us. The first thing we need
OL,15,Fto do is to be efficient.
OL,17,F"Once you have got efficiency in the
OL,18,Fsystem you can then layer on different
OL,19,Fthings to help the process."
