OL,3,CMinister: 'Funding for Jersey's health
OL,4,Cservice may have to change'
OL,6,FThe minister is looking at the
OL,7,Fprospect of having someone in charge
OL,8,Fof the health service in its entirety.
OL,10,FHe also wants to address spending
OL,11,Fwhich hit #303 million in 2023 and is
OL,12,Fexpected to reach #329 million this
OL,13,Fyear just to keep the current services
OL,14,Frunning.
OL,16,FThat figure is more than a quarter of
OL,17,Fthe entire States' budget.
