OL,3,CMinister: 'Funding for Jersey's health
OL,4,Cservice may have to change'
OL,6,FThe minister says that the Government
OL,7,Fhas looked at other healthcare funding
OL,8,Fmodels - a few global examples are
OL,9,Flisted below:
OL,11,FThe Beveridge Model (National Health
OL,12,FService)
OL,14,FFunded by taxes, there are no out-of-
OL,15,Fpocket fees for patients or any cost-
OL,16,Fsharing. Everyone who is a tax-paying
OL,17,Fcitizen is guaranteed the same access
OL,18,Fto care and nobody will ever receive a
OL,19,Fmedical bill.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G5/12
