OL,3,CMinister: 'Funding for Jersey's health
OL,4,Cservice may have to change'
OL,6,FIn some countries such as France,
OL,7,Fthere is a single insurer.
OL,9,FCare is subsidised for those who are
OL,10,Funemployed and receive pensions.
OL,12,FThe primary criticism of the Bismarck
OL,13,FModel is how to provide care for those
OL,14,Fwho are unable to work or can't afford
OL,15,Fcontributions, including ageing
OL,16,Fpopulations and the imbalance between
OL,17,Fretirees and employees.
OL,19,FThe National Health Insurance Model
