OL,3,CMinister: 'Funding for Jersey's health
OL,4,Cservice may have to change'
OL,6,FThis option blends different aspects
OL,7,Fof both the Beveridge Model and the
OL,8,FBismarck Model together.
OL,10,FFirst, like the Beveridge model, the
OL,11,FGovernment acts as the single-payer
OL,12,Ffor medical procedures. However, like
OL,13,Fthe Bismarck model, providers are
OL,14,Fprivate.
OL,16,FThe National Health Insurance Model is
OL,17,Fdriven by private providers but the
OL,18,Fpayments come from a government-run
OL,19,Finsurance program that every citizen
OL,20,Fpays into.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G9/12
