OL,3,CMinister: 'Funding for Jersey's health
OL,4,Cservice may have to change'
OL,6,FEssentially, it is universal insurance
OL,7,Fthat does not make a profit or deny
OL,8,Fclaims.
OL,10,FSince there is no need for marketing,
OL,11,Fno financial motive to deny claims,
OL,12,Fand no concern for profit, it is
OL,13,Fcheaper and simpler to navigate.
OL,15,FThis balance between private and
OL,16,Fpublic gives hospitals and providers
OL,17,Fmore freedom without the frustrating
OL,18,Fcomplexity of insurance plans and
OL,19,Fpolicies.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws        G10/12
